DISORDER.

25:08.640 --> 25:09.698
- WHERE HAVE I HEARD
THAT TERM BEFORE?

25:09.740 --> 25:11.037
- DPD?
- NO.

25:11.070 --> 25:12.662
THE DEPERSONALIZATION THING.

25:12.710 --> 25:15.201
- IT'S A DISORDER
CHARACTERIZED

25:15.240 --> 25:18.801
