HER NEXT MOVE

25:40.370 --> 25:42.634
TO BE MORE LOGICAL
THAN EMOTIONAL.

25:42.670 --> 25:44.934
- DO YOU, DECLAN?

25:44.970 --> 25:46.107
- YOU GOT IT.

