BACK AT THE STATION AT 4:00.

25:49.110 --> 25:51.078
- ALL RIGHT,
LET'S BREAK TILL THEN.

25:51.110 --> 25:52.907
- ALL RIGHT,
I'LL SEE YOU GUYS THERE.

25:52.950 --> 25:57.171
- NOT IF WE SEE YOU
FIRST, BUDDY.

25:57.220 --> 26:00.246
- WHAT DO YOU GOT?
- THREE THINGS.

26:00.290 --> 26:03.851
ONE, I'M NOT THE ONLY CLOSET
CHICK-LIT LOVER AROUND HERE.

26:03.890 --> 26:06.688
TWO, DECLAN IS A COMPLETE FRAUD.

26:06.730 --> 26:10.291
AND "H," HE MAY JUST
BE OUR MURDERER.

26:19.310 --> 26:20.459
WHILE YOU WERE ANNOYINGLY
TALKING TO KIM

26:20.510 --> 26:23.274
FOR THE NINTH TIME TODAY,
I WAS ON THE PHONE WITH HARVARD,

26:23.310 --> 26:25.847
WHO SAID THAT THERE IS NO RECORD
