TO ADMIT THAT.

26:48.870 --> 26:50.394
DECLAN HAD THE SAME
INFORMATION I DID.

26:50.440 --> 26:52.635
HE JUST LET ME GET THERE FIRST.

26:52.670 --> 26:55.207
I KNOW THIS MAN BECAUSE HE ALSO
LISTENED TO INTERNITY.

26:55.240 --> 26:56.730
- OR READ.

26:56.780 --> 26:58.008
- I JUST SAID HE DIDN'T GO
TO HARVARD, GUS.

26:58.050 --> 26:59.176
- I DON'T KNOW, SHAWN.

26:59.210 --> 27:00.404
MAYBE YOU HAVE A THING
AGAINST PROFILERS.

27:00.450 --> 27:01.974
- HE'S GUILTY, ALL RIGHT?

27:02.020 --> 27:03.647
AND FOR THE RECORD,
LASSIE AGREES.

27:03.690 --> 27:06.079
