- WHY WOULD YOU CONSULT LASSIE?

27:06.120 --> 27:09.351
- BECAUSE UNLIKE YOU AND JULES,
HE'S NOT SMITTEN WITH THIS GUY.

27:09.390 --> 27:10.357
- I'M NOT SMITTEN.

27:10.390 --> 27:11.755
- YOU'RE JIMMY SMITTEN.

27:11.790 --> 27:13.655
TRUST ME, GUS.

27:13.700 --> 27:16.897
EVERYTHING YOU THINK YOU KNOW
ABOUT THIS GUY IS A LIE.

27:22.740 --> 27:24.731
- WHERE THE HECK IS HE GOING?

27:31.310 --> 27:33.403
ONCE AGAIN,
WE'RE ON THE VERGE OF TRYING

27:33.450 --> 27:35.418
TO APPREHEND A POTENTIAL KILLER
WITHOUT A WEAPON.

27:35.450 --> 27:36.917
- DON'T WORRY.

27:36.950 --> 27:39.214
I CAME PREPARED THIS TIME.

27:39.250 --> 27:42.253
[indistinct whispering]

27:46.760 --> 27:48.421
HELLO, DECLAN.

27:48.460 --> 27:50.894
- HEY, GUYS.

27:50.930 --> 27:54.696
WELCOME TO THE BARBECUE
I DIDN'T KNOW I WAS THROWING.

27:54.740 --> 27:56.731
COME ON IN.

28:01.810 --> 28:03.437
- SWEET PLACE.

28:03.480 --> 28:04.879
- WHOSE IS IT, DECLAN?

28:04.910 --> 28:06.343
