ALL YOUR PROFILER MONEY?

28:13.860 --> 28:15.487
- I THINK HE'S TELLING
THE TRUTH, SHAWN.

28:15.520 --> 28:16.680
- COME ON, GUS.

28:16.720 --> 28:19.848
