28:30.440 --> 28:33.500
- THAT PAINTING KIND OF MAKES
YOU LOOK LIKE JOHN STAMOS.

28:33.540 --> 28:35.804
- THANK YOU.

28:35.840 --> 28:37.501
WHEN DO YOU PLAN ON DROPPING
THAT GRILL FORK?

28:37.540 --> 28:41.112
- SOON AS YOU AGREE
TO TELL US YOUR REAL STORY.

28:41.150 --> 28:43.471
- FAIR ENOUGH.

28:43.520 --> 28:45.010
WALK WITH ME, GENTLEMEN.

28:45.050 --> 28:47.757
- * WHEN THEY DO I'LL BE
RIGHT BEHIND YOU *

