- SO ABOUT SIX YEARS AGO,
I WAS JUST RUNNING

28:50.120 --> 28:52.122
A SMALL HEDGE FUND
AND I JUST DECIDED

28:52.160 --> 28:54.048
TO MAKE A BUNCH OF BETS
AGAINST THE HOUSING MARKET.

28:54.100 --> 28:55.522
