EXCUSE ME!
- YES?

29:08.940 --> 29:11.773
- WHY IS THERE A MAN WHO LOOKS
EXACTLY LIKE CURT SMITH

29:11.810 --> 29:13.846
FROM TEARS FOR FEARS PLAYING
AN ACOUSTIC SET

29:13.880 --> 29:16.371
NEXT TO THAT TREE
AND YOUR SWIMMING POOL?

29:16.420 --> 29:18.217
- I'M SORRY.
