29:18.250 --> 29:19.786
CURT, MEET SHAWN AND GUS.

29:19.820 --> 29:21.082
- AFTERNOON, GENTLEMEN.

29:21.120 --> 29:23.418
- OH, DEAR GOD.
IT'S YOU.

29:23.460 --> 29:25.485
THE REAL YOU.
THE FLESHY YOU.

29:25.530 --> 29:26.781
I LOVE YOU.

29:26.830 --> 29:28.024
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA

29:28.060 --> 29:31.268
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOU?

29:31.300 --> 29:32.961
- I THINK I DO NOW.

