HERE.

29:53.960 --> 29:56.417
ANYWAY, SO THERE I WAS
IN MY LATE 30$,

29:56.460 --> 29:57.825
NEVER HAVING TO WORRY
ABOUT MONEY AGAIN,

29:57.860 --> 29:59.350
SO I DECIDED TO PURSUE
THE CHILDHOOD DREAM.

29:59.390 --> 30:01.392
- CRIMINAL PROFILER?
- NO, SUSHI CHEF.

