AND I KNEW ALL THIS STUFF
ABOUT PSYCHOLOGY

30:08.900 --> 30:10.458
'CAUSE MY DAD USED
TO BE A THERAPIST.

30:10.500 --> 30:11.865
- SOUNDS FAMILIAR.

30:11.910 --> 30:13.161
- SO I FUDGED A FEW
QUALIFICATIONS

30:13.210 --> 30:15.371
