- CURT, PLEASE!

30:18.480 --> 30:22.041
WHAT DID I SAY ABOUT
GOING OFF BOOK?

30:22.080 --> 30:24.583
- * AND I FIND IT
KIND OF FUNNY *

30:24.620 --> 30:27.111
* I FIND IT KIND OF SAD

30:27.150 --> 30:29.414
- LISTEN, YOU GUYS AREN'T GONNA
TELL CHIEF VICK, ARE YOU?

30:29.460 --> 30:31.257
- NO, BUT YOU BETTER
DAMN WELL TELL JULIET.

30:31.290 --> 30:32.587
SHE'S INTO YOU.
- COOL, MAN.

30:32.630 --> 30:34.598
