YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

31:06.530 --> 31:08.498
- OH, COME ON, SHAWN.

31:08.530 --> 31:10.350
I'VE BEEN ON TO YOU SINCE
THE BEGINNING.

31:10.400 --> 31:12.493
DON'T FORGET WE READ
THE SAME BOOKS.

31:12.530 --> 31:14.430
- * THEY HAVE
THE SAME TASTE IN-- *

31:14.470 --> 31:15.494
- CURT, FOR CHRISSAKE.

31:15.540 --> 31:17.167
I SAY ONE THING,
YOU DO THE OTHER.

31:17.200 --> 31:18.428
- DON'T SWEAT IT.
I STILL LOVE YOU.

31:18.470 --> 31:20.461
- COULD YOU JUST STOP SAYING
YOU LOVE ME?

31:20.510 --> 31:22.501
- DONE AND DONE.

31:22.540 --> 31:24.508
I DO THOUGH, LOVE YOU,
THAT IS.

31:24.550 --> 31:25.539
- SHAWN?
- WHAT?

31:25.580 --> 31:28.276
I LOVE CURT SMITH
AND I DON'T CARE WHO KNOWS.

31:28.320 --> 31:30.140
I WILL SING IT
FROM THE ROOFTOPS, GUS.

31:30.180 --> 31:32.683
- * EVERYBODY

31:32.720 --> 31:37.453
* WANTS TO RULE THE WORLD

31:37.490 --> 31:43.497
*

31:47.570 --> 31:49.367
- DAD, YOU HAVE GOT
TO FIRE THIS GUY.

31:49.400 --> 31:50.389
HE IS A FRAUD.

31:50.440 --> 31:51.532
- SO ARE YOU.

31:51.570 --> 31:52.707
- YEAH, BUT I'M
A PRODUCTIVE ONE.

31:52.740 --> 31:53.934
- SO IS HE.

31:53.980 --> 31:55.333
- AND HE KNOWS TEARS FOR FEARS.

31:55.380 --> 31:56.472
- HALF. HE KNOWS HALF
OF TEARS FOR FEARS.

31:56.510 --> 31:58.205
THE HALF THAT I LOVE.
THE HALF THAT I WOULD DO ANY--

31:58.250 --> 31:59.569
- SHAWN.

31:59.610 --> 32:01.510
- ALL RIGHT, LOOK, SHAWN,
I CAN'T JUST FIRE HIM.

32:01.550 --> 32:03.177
THERE ARE NO LEGAL REQUIREMENTS
ONE NEEDS

32:03.220 --> 32:04.619
TO CALL THEMSELVES
A CRIMINAL PROFILER.

32:06.550 --> 32:07.585
IT WORKED, OKAY?

32:07.620 --> 32:08.985
- HE GETS RESULTS.

32:09.020 --> 32:10.612
AND WHY DON'T YOU QUIT
COMPLAINING TO ME,

32:10.660 --> 32:12.218
GET YOUR ASS OUT
THERE LIKE DECLAN,

32:12.260 --> 32:13.727
AND START TRACKING DOWN
OUR MURDERER?

32:13.760 --> 32:15.648
- YOU'RE LOVING THIS,
AREN'T YOU?

32:15.700 --> 32:17.122
- THEY JUST SPOTTED
CATHERINE BICKS

32:17.160 --> 32:20.027
WALKING THROUGH
A PARKING GARAGE.

32:35.650 --> 32:36.969
- AHH.

32:37.020 --> 32:38.612
- UH-OH.

32:38.650 --> 32:39.639
- WE WERE RIGHT, SPENCER.

32:39.690 --> 32:42.215
DECLAN RAND,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

32:42.260 --> 32:45.650
FOR THE MURDER
OF CATHERINE BICKS.

32:54.240 --> 32:58.006
- YOU, TAKE THIS JOKER DOWN
TO INTERROGATION ROOM "A."

33:03.280 --> 33:04.747
- YEP.

33:04.780 --> 33:06.304
I ALWAYS KNEW HE
WAS A NO-GOOD MURDERER.

33:06.350 --> 33:08.614
- SHAWN, YOU KNOW VERY WELL
HE DIDN'T DO IT.

33:08.650 --> 33:10.675
- FINE.
I WAS WRONG, PROBABLY.

33:10.720 --> 33:12.312
THE BEST KIND OF WRONG.

33:12.350 --> 33:15.285
THE KIND THAT MAKES YOU FEEL
GOOD ABOUT YOURSELF.

33:15.320 --> 33:17.015
WHAT, GUS?
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

33:17.060 --> 33:18.288
- HELP PROVE HIS INNOCENCE.

33:18.330 --> 33:20.525
- ALL RIGHT, STARTING SUNDAY
AFTER THE WEDDING.

33:20.560 --> 33:22.528
- SHAWN.

33:22.560 --> 33:26.166
- OKAY.

33:26.200 --> 33:28.031
LASSIE?
- WHAT?

33:28.070 --> 33:29.560
- BEFORE YOU START YOUR
LEGALLY-QUESTIONABLE

33:29.600 --> 33:31.261
INTERROGATION TECHNIQUES,
MAY WE HAVE

33:31.310 --> 33:33.039
FIVE MINUTES WITH DECLAN?

33:33.070 --> 33:35.106
- ALL RIGHT,
YOU'VE GOT FIVE MINUTES,

33:35.140 --> 33:36.471
BUT THEN YOU TELL HIM
I'M COMING

33:36.510 --> 33:39.070
AND HELL IS COMING WITH ME.

33:39.110 --> 33:43.217
- ALL RIGHT, WHAT?

33:43.250 --> 33:45.138
HEY.

33:45.190 --> 33:47.408
- GUYS, I'M SO GLAD YOU'RE HERE.

33:47.450 --> 33:49.281
WILL YOU DO ME A HUGE FAVOR?

33:49.320 --> 33:50.582
WILL YOU CHECK IN ON CURT
AND MAKE SURE

33:50.620 --> 33:52.178
HE ISN'T THROWING A BENDER?

33:52.230 --> 33:53.754
'CAUSE I THINK HE AND THAT
DUDE FROM CROWDED HOUSE--

33:53.790 --> 33:55.121
I THINK THEY'RE PLOTTING
SOMETHING.

33:55.160 --> 33:56.320
- NEIL FINN?

33:56.360 --> 33:57.497
THERE'S NO WAY WE'RE MISSING
THAT.

33:57.530 --> 33:58.519
- WHAT HAPPENED IN THAT GARAGE?

33:58.570 --> 34:00.720
- I DON'T KNOW.

34:00.770 --> 34:03.238
I HEARD ON THE POLICE RADIO
CATHERINE WAS SPOTTED THERE.

34:03.270 --> 34:05.306
I WANTED TO BE THERE FIRST
TO SHOW YOU UP A LITTLE,

34:05.340 --> 34:07.365
AND THEN I ARRIVED
TO FIND HER LAYING DEAD.

34:07.410 --> 34:10.231
BUT WHY WOULD THE POLICE THINK
I WAS A MURDERER?

34:10.280 --> 34:12.271
- THAT IS NOT IMPORTANT
RIGHT NOW.

34:12.310 --> 34:14.141
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHO ELSE IT MAY HAVE BEEN?

34:14.180 --> 34:15.545
- I WISH.
THERE'S NO PATTERN

34:15.580 --> 34:16.774
TO THE MURDERS ANYMORE.

34:16.820 --> 34:18.287
THE FIRST THREE WERE POISONED

34:18.320 --> 34:19.810
AND CATHERINE DIED FROM
A BLOW TO THE HEAD.

34:19.850 --> 34:21.488
- YEAH, THAT'S WEIRD.
- YEAH, AND GET THIS.

34:21.520 --> 34:22.851
CATHERINE ALMOST
APPEARED HEALTHIER

34:22.890 --> 34:24.482
THAN SHE DID WHEN
WE FIRST SAW HER.

34:24.530 --> 34:30.298
YOU KNOW,
MINUS THE WHOLE DEAD THING.

34:30.330 --> 34:32.560
- I'VE GOT SOMETHING.

34:32.600 --> 34:34.363
- OH, COME ON, SHAWN.
IT'S JUST US.

34:34.400 --> 34:35.799
THERE'S NO NEED
FOR THIS ANYMORE.

34:35.840 --> 34:37.091
- SERIOUSLY?
YOU'RE CHALLENGING ME RIGHT NOW?

34:37.140 --> 34:38.129
I'M TRYING TO HELP YOU.

34:38.170 --> 34:39.239
- I JUST THOUGHT
IT WAS RIDICULOUS.

34:39.270 --> 34:40.259
- SO IS YOUR FACE.

34:40.310 --> 34:42.369
- OKAY, SORRY.
WHAT'D YOU GET?

34:42.410 --> 34:44.275
- STAY TUNED.

34:44.310 --> 34:45.299
COME ON, GUS, LET'S GO
HAVE A CONVERSATION

34:45.350 --> 34:46.647
WITH OUR FAVORITE WEIRDO.

34:46.680 --> 34:48.216
- I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU DO IT,
SHAWN,

34:48.250 --> 34:49.717
BUT YOU WERE SPOT ON.

34:49.750 --> 34:51.115
- ABOUT WHAT?

34:51.150 --> 34:52.082
- A LOT OF THINGS.

34:52.120 --> 34:54.213
MY WIFE, FOR EXAMPLE,
WASN'T JUST FRIENDS

34:54.260 --> 34:56.182
WITH THAT COLLEGE FRESHMAN,
AND CATHERINE HERE

34:56.220 --> 34:58.154
WASN'T SUFFERING FROM CIRRHOSIS
OF THE LIVER.

34:58.190 --> 35:00.283
IN FACT, PRIOR TO THE HEAD
TRAUMA THAT ENDED HER LIFE,

35:00.330 --> 35:02.298
SHE WAS THE MODEL OF HEALTH.

35:02.330 --> 35:04.719
- SHE APPLIED MAKEUP UNDER HER
EYES THE DAY THAT WE SAW HER

35:04.770 --> 35:06.169
IN ORDER TO APPEAR SICK.

35:06.200 --> 35:07.690
_- WHY?
[scoffs]

35:07.730 --> 35:09.334
SAME REASON
A MIDDLE-AGED WOMAN

35:09.370 --> 35:10.598
SLEEPS WITH
A STAR LACROSSE PLAYER.

35:10.640 --> 35:12.335
- THOSE ARE COMPLETELY
UNRELATED, WOODY.

35:12.370 --> 35:15.305
- AND BETTER YET, WHY WOULD SHE
WANT TO GET ON A LIST

35:15.340 --> 35:16.876
FOR A NEW LIVER WHEN HERS
WAS PERFECT LY HEALTHY?

35:16.910 --> 35:18.901
- HOW DID SHE GET ON
IS THE BETTER QUESTION.

35:18.950 --> 35:21.714
THERE'S AN INTENSE SCREENING
PROCESS ONE HAS TO GO THROUGH.

35:21.750 --> 35:25.481
THERE IS NO WAY SOMEONE THAT
HEALTHY WOULD GET THAT FAR.

35:25.520 --> 35:27.613
- WOODY, IS SHE A LEFTY
OR A RIGHTY?

35:27.650 --> 35:29.311
- OH, DEFINITELY A RIGHTY.

35:29.360 --> 35:34.320
MUSCLES IN THAT ARM
ARE MUCH MORE DEVELOPED.

35:34.360 --> 35:37.488
- THAT WASN'T CATHERINE
IN THE PHOTO.

35:37.530 --> 35:39.760
WHO USES THE PARKING GARAGE
WHERE SHE WAS KILLED?

35:39.800 --> 35:42.189
- AN APARTMENT COMPLEX, WHY?
- I'LL TELL YOU ON THE WAY.

35:42.240 --> 35:44.208
YOUR WIFE'S ALSO SLEEPING
WITH HER PERSONAL TRAINER.

35:44.240 --> 35:46.538
- YEAH, IT'S OKAY.
I APPROVED THAT ONE.

35:51.710 --> 35:56.170
- I'M SENSING THE KILLER
IS IN APARTMENT FIVE.

35:56.220 --> 35:58.438
- YOU POSITIVE ABOUT THIS?
- ABSOLUTELY.

35:58.490 --> 36:01.288
- OPEN UP!

36:01.320 --> 36:03.481
BETTER BE RIGHT ABOUT THIS,
SPENCER.

36:09.230 --> 36:11.824
PUT YOUR HANDS UP.

36:11.870 --> 36:12.962
PUT YOUR HANDS IN THE AIR.

36:13.000 --> 36:16.197
PUT 'EM UP!

36:25.550 --> 36:26.505
- CATHERINE?

36:26.550 --> 36:28.313
- WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON?

36:28.350 --> 36:30.238
- NOT CATHERINE.

36:30.280 --> 36:31.417
THIS IS MADDY.

36:31.450 --> 36:34.248
- HER SISTER.
- EXACTLY.

36:34.290 --> 36:37.453
SEE, MADDY IS THE ONE WITH
THE SEVERE LIVER PROBLEMS.

36:37.490 --> 36:40.323
BUT SHE CAN'T QUALIFY
FOR A TRANSPLANT LIST

36:40.360 --> 36:41.725
ON ACCOUNT OF HER ALCOHOLISM.

36:41.760 --> 36:42.897
- I'M NOT AN ALCOHOLIC.

36:42.930 --> 36:44.693
- CLEARLY.
MY APOLOGIES.

36:44.730 --> 36:47.290
- SO SHE AND CATHERINE
HATCHED A PLAN.

36:47.330 --> 36:49.764
- MADDY TOOK HER
SISTER'S I.D. TO A DOCTOR

36:49.800 --> 36:51.438
SO SHE COULD GET PUT
ON THE LIST.

36:51.470 --> 36:52.607
- AS CATHERINE.

36:52.640 --> 36:53.959
NOW ALL SHE HAD TO DO WAS WAIT

36:54.010 --> 36:55.898
FOR HER NUMBER TO BE CALLED AND
HER LIFE WOULD BE SAVED.

36:55.940 --> 36:57.999
- BUT MADDY WAS GETTING SICKER
AND MORE IMPATIENT.

36:58.040 --> 37:00.679
WHEN CATHERINE LEFT THE COUNTRY,
SHE DECIDED

37:00.710 --> 37:02.644
TO START KILLING PEOPLE
ON THE LIST ABOVE HER,

37:02.680 --> 37:04.580
SO THAT SHE COULD MOVE UP.

37:04.620 --> 37:07.839
- THEY HAD ALL LIVED LONG LIVES.

37:07.890 --> 37:09.755
- NOT THE MOST SYMPATHETIC
DEFENSE.

37:09.790 --> 37:12.258
- THEN CATHERINE GOT HOME,
FOUND OUT WHAT SHE WAS DOING.

37:12.290 --> 37:14.952
SHE CONFRONTED YOU
IN THAT PARKING GARAGE.

37:15.000 --> 37:16.058
- WE HAVE GOT
TO GO TO THE COPS.

37:16.100 --> 37:18.989
- WE ARE NOT GOING TO
THE COPS AND IF YOU THINK--

37:19.030 --> 37:20.429
- YOU ARE SO SELFISH!

37:20.470 --> 37:22.597
- I WILL NOT LET YOU!

37:22.640 --> 37:24.665
- AND IN A RAGE,
YOU PUSHED HER DOWN.

37:24.710 --> 37:25.802
SHE BANGED HER HEAD.

37:25.840 --> 37:26.864
SHE DIED.

37:26.910 --> 37:29.572
- CATHERINE?

37:29.610 --> 37:32.374
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

37:32.410 --> 37:34.412
- YOU PUSHED HER DOWN.

37:34.450 --> 37:35.576
SHE BANGED HER HEAD.

37:35.620 --> 37:37.417
- SHAWN.

37:37.450 --> 37:41.045
A COMMON SIDE EFFECT OF SEVERE
LIVER FAILURE IS PSYCHOSIS.

37:41.090 --> 37:44.548
SHE PROBABLY DOESN'T EVEN
KNOW WHAT SHE'S DOING.

37:44.590 --> 37:48.651
- [sobbing]

37:53.330 --> 37:55.560
- I OWE YOU HUGE.

37:55.600 --> 37:57.488
NO, I MEAN HUGE, SHAWN.

37:57.540 --> 37:59.303
AND AS A TOKEN
OF MY APPRECIATION,

37:59.340 --> 38:01.331
I'M GONNA LOAN OUT CURT SMITH
FOR YOUR BUDDY'S WEDDING.

38:01.380 --> 38:02.972
- WHAT?
NOW DON'T PLAY WITH ME.

38:03.010 --> 38:04.807
- FAIR WARNING THOUGH.
HE'S AN ANGRY DRUNK.

38:04.850 --> 38:06.806
I MEAN, WHO THROWS
A KEYTAR INTO A JACUZZI?

38:06.850 --> 38:08.317
- OH, THAT'S MONEY.

38:08.350 --> 38:09.874
- LISTEN.

38:09.920 --> 38:12.343
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT WHAT
YOU'RE SAYING ABOUT JULIET,

38:12.390 --> 38:15.314
AND IT'S SILLY FOR ANYONE
TO KEEP A GIANT SECRET

38:15.360 --> 38:17.055
ABOUT THEMSELVES FROM SOMEONE
THEY COULD POTENTIALLY

38:17.090 --> 38:18.489
FALL FOR, YOU KNOW?

38:18.530 --> 38:20.851
- I DO, ACTUALLY.

38:20.890 --> 38:23.688
- SO I'M GONNA COME CLEAN.
- REALLY?

38:23.730 --> 38:26.096
'CAUSE I WAS THINKING ABOUT
DOING THE SAME THING.

38:26.130 --> 38:28.098
- REALLY?
- YEAH.

38:28.130 --> 38:30.997
I WAS THINKING
MAYBE IT'S TIME.

38:31.040 --> 38:34.703
- TIME FOR WHAT?

38:34.740 --> 38:39.609
- JULES.

38:39.650 --> 38:41.914
UH...

38:41.950 --> 38:46.011
HERE'S THE THING.

38:46.050 --> 38:48.416
[sighs]

38:48.460 --> 38:50.951
WILL YOU TAKE A WALK WITH ME?

38:50.990 --> 38:53.982
CAN YOU GIVE US A SEC?

38:54.030 --> 38:55.998
- I'M A FRAUD.

38:56.030 --> 38:58.624
- WHAT?

38:58.670 --> 39:01.764
- I DON'T HAVE ANY, UH,

39:01.800 --> 39:03.734
FANCY DEGREES FROM HARVARD

39:03.770 --> 39:06.739
OR YEARS OF EXPERIENCE
AS A PROFILER.

39:06.770 --> 39:09.477
I'M JUST A GUY WITH A LITTLE
KNOWLEDGE OF PSYCHOLOGY

39:09.510 --> 39:12.104
AND A LOVE FOR CATCHING
BAD GUYS.

39:12.150 --> 39:14.106
THIS WHOLE PERSONA I'VE
BEEN PUTTING ON IS JUST--

39:14.150 --> 39:15.139
IT'S A COMPLETE FAKE
AND I JUST THOUGHT

39:15.180 --> 39:16.647
IT WAS IMPORTANT
TO TELL YOU THIS,

39:16.680 --> 39:18.079
'CAUSE YOU STRIKE ME
AS THE KIND OF PERSON

39:18.120 --> 39:19.712
WHO APPRECIATES HON ESTY.

39:19.750 --> 39:21.809
- WOW.

39:21.860 --> 39:23.111
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

39:23.160 --> 39:28.086
- WELL, LET'S TALK ABOUT IT.

39:28.130 --> 39:31.896
OR NOT.

39:31.930 --> 39:35.468
WELL, THAT DIDN'T GO VERY WELL,
DID IT, SHAWN?

39:35.500 --> 39:37.058
- SHH.
JUST GIVE ME ONE SECOND, DECK.

39:37.100 --> 39:39.933
LET ME JUST--ONE SECOND
HERE AND...

39:39.970 --> 39:41.608
DONE.

39:41.640 --> 39:43.005
THIS IS ACTUALLY
THE FIRST TIME

39:43.040 --> 39:44.746
THAT I'M GLAD YOU
BEAT ME TO THE PUNCH.

39:44.780 --> 39:46.099
I CAN'T THANK YOU ENOUGH, MAN.

39:46.150 --> 39:48.846
- WELL, YOU'LL GET OTHER
OPPORTUNITIES TO TALK TO HER.

39:48.880 --> 39:50.768
ME?
NOT SO MUCH.

39:50.820 --> 39:53.744
- LISTEN, DECLAN...

39:53.790 --> 39:55.587
YOU'RE RIGHT ABOUT ONE THING.

39:55.620 --> 39:58.851
THERE'S NOTHING I VALUE
MORE THAN HONESTY

39:58.890 --> 40:02.121
AND IT DOES REALLY BOTHER ME
THAT YOU WOULD LIE LIKE THAT,

40:02.160 --> 40:05.789
BUT I'M ALSO JUST BLOWN AWAY
THAT YOU COULD BE

40:05.830 --> 40:08.435
JUST SO FORTHCOMING.

40:08.470 --> 40:10.768
TOOK A LOT OF GUTS.

40:10.800 --> 40:12.734
- SHOULD WE TALK IT OUT
OVER COFFEE?

40:12.770 --> 40:14.203
- I DON'T THINK SO.

40:14.240 --> 40:16.504
- SURE.

40:16.540 --> 40:19.509
BUT IF YOU'RE SITTING
ON ANY OTHER LIFE SECRETS,

40:19.550 --> 40:21.438
NOW IS THE TIME TO TELL ME.

40:21.480 --> 40:26.816
- OKAY.

40:26.850 --> 40:30.058
I'M REALLY RICH.

40:30.090 --> 40:33.423
- OKAY, I CAN DEAL WITH THAT.

40:39.230 --> 40:41.425
[cell phone vibrates]

40:52.810 --> 40:57.042
- * SO GLAD WE'VE
ALMOST MADE IT *

40:57.080 --> 40:59.810
* $0--

41:03.890 --> 41:05.824
- WOW.

41:05.860 --> 41:07.851
CURT'S REALLY LOSING IT.

41:07.890 --> 41:10.222
- * BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH

41:10.260 --> 41:14.765
* WANTS TO RULE THE...

41:14.800 --> 41:18.167
* WORLD

41:18.200 --> 41:19.667
- GUS, THERE YOU ARE.

41:19.710 --> 41:21.063
YOU MISSED THE ENTIRE CEREMONY.

41:21.110 --> 41:22.702
WHERE'S KIM?

41:22.740 --> 41:23.729
- MAN, WE BROKE UP.

41:23.780 --> 41:25.270
- WHAT?
YOU'RE KIDDING ME.

41:25.310 --> 41:26.675
WHAT HAPPENED?
- I DON'T KNOW.

41:26.710 --> 41:27.972
WE WERE OUT HAVING
A NICE LUNCH TODAY,

41:28.010 --> 41:29.272
WHEN OUT OF NOWHERE SHE GOES,

41:29.320 --> 41:30.810
"IT'S LIKE WE DON'T KNOW
EACH OTHER ANYMORE."

41:30.850 --> 41:33.216
- THAT'S BECAUSE AS
OF A WEEK AGO, YOU DIDN'T.

41:33.250 --> 41:34.558
- MAN, THIS SUCKS.

41:34.590 --> 41:35.682
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M SINGLE AGAIN.

41:35.720 --> 41:36.709
- YOU KNOW WHO CAN?

41:36.760 --> 41:38.284
ANYONE WHO MET YOU
EIGHT DAYS AGO.

41:38.320 --> 41:40.254
- HOW ABOUT SHOWING SOME
COMPASSION, SHAWN?

41:40.290 --> 41:41.848
- ABSOLUTELY NOT.
THAT WHOLE THING WAS ABSURD.

41:41.900 --> 41:43.197
YOU'RE A RIDICULOUS PERSON.

41:43.230 --> 41:45.767
- YOU'RE A RIDICULOUS PERSON.
HOW ABOUT THAT?

41:45.800 --> 41:46.926
WHAT'S THE LATEST WITH GINA?

41:46.970 --> 41:48.597
HAS SHE TRIED TO KILL YOU YET

41:48.640 --> 41:49.436
FOR UNINVITING HER
TO THIS WEDDING?

41:49.470 --> 41:52.132
- NO, BECAUSE I CAME UP
WITH A FIX.

41:52.170 --> 41:53.762
- THIS BUFFET IS SO GOOD.

41:53.810 --> 41:54.834
HI, GUS.

41:54.880 --> 41:56.074
- HELLO, GINA.

41:56.110 --> 41:57.771
YOU HAVE PROBLEMS.
- HELP ME.

41:57.810 --> 41:59.949
- YOU HAVE GOT TO TRY THE
BRUSCHETTA, SHAWN, SERIOUSLY.

41:59.980 --> 42:01.868
- I'D REALLY PREFER NOT TO.

42:01.920 --> 42:03.547
- OH, WELL, THEN I'LL BE
THE ONLY ONE WITH GARLIC BREATH

42:03.580 --> 42:05.286
AND IT'LL BE REALLY GROSS
WHEN WE MAKE OUT LATER.

42:05.320 --> 42:07.117
- YES, IT WILL.

42:07.150 --> 42:10.654
- MMM.

42:10.690 --> 42:11.884
- OH.

42:11.930 --> 42:13.022
OH!

42:13.060 --> 42:16.223
- * HE HAD A GIFT INVOLVING

42:16.260 --> 42:19.195
* PROBLEM SOLVING

42:19.230 --> 42:20.197
* NEVER BACKING DOWN

42:20.230 --> 42:21.697
- IT'S REALLY GARLIC-Y.
UGH!

